      <format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="65721-102">枚举表示可为<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal>控件中的内容的呈现方式指定的模式。 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LiteralMode></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="65721-102">The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LiteralMode> enumeration represents the modes that you can specify for how the content in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal> control is rendered.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="65721-103">属性使用这些枚举值在<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal>控件中设置<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A>属性内容的行为。 <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Mode%2A></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="65721-103">The <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Mode%2A> property uses these enumeration values to set the behavior of the contents of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A> property in a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal> control.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="65721-104">如果指定`PassThrough`, 则会将<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A>属性的全部内容传递到设备或浏览器, 而不进行任何修改。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="65721-104">If you specify `PassThrough`, the entire contents of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A> property are passed to the device or browser without any modifications.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="65721-105">例如, 如果<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal>控件的<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A>属性包含`<hr>`标记, 则会将其发送到所有设备和浏览器, 无论它是否受支持。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="65721-105">For example, if the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A> property of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal> control contains an `<hr>` tag, it is sent to all devices and browsers regardless of whether it is supported.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="65721-106">如果指定`Encode`, 则在<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A>呈现之前, 属性的内容将转换为 HTML 编码的字符串。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="65721-106">If you specify `Encode`, the contents for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A> property are converted into an HTML-encoded string before rendering.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="65721-107">例如, 如果<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal>控件的<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A>属性包含`<hr>`标记, 则该属性将转换为`&lt;hr&gt;`并发送到设备或浏览器。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="65721-107">For example, if the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A> property of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal> control contains an `<hr>` tag, it will be converted to `&lt;hr&gt;` and sent to the device or browser.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="65721-108">如果指定`Transform`, <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A>属性的呈现行为取决于所呈现的标记的类型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="65721-108">If you specify `Transform`, the rendering behavior of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A> property depends on the type of markup being rendered.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="65721-109">为支持 HTML 或 XHTML 的设备或浏览器呈现控件时,指定转换将产生与指定PassThrough相同的行为。<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="65721-109">When the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal> control is rendered for a device or browser that supports HTML or XHTML, specifying Transform produces the same behavior as specifying PassThrough.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="65721-110">为请求浏览器呈现<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A>属性的所有标记和元素。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="65721-110">All markup tags and elements for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A> property are rendered for the requesting browser.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="65721-111">如果为除 HTML 或 XHTML 之外的标记语言 (如 WML 或 cHTML) 呈现控件,则可以使用转换值来删除不支持的标记元素。<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LiteralMode.PassThrough></span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="65721-111">When the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LiteralMode.PassThrough> control is rendered for a markup language other than HTML or XHTML, such as WML or cHTML, you can use the Transform value to remove unsupported markup elements.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="65721-112">在这种情况下, 不会为控件呈现<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A>在目标标记语言中不支持的属性的任何标记语言元素。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="65721-112">In this case, any markup-language elements of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A> property that are not supported in the targeted markup language are not rendered for the control.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="65721-113">例如, 如果<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LiteralMode.Transform>控件的<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A>属性包含`<hr>`标记, 则在将内容发送到 WML 设备之前, 将删除该标记。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="65721-113">For example, if the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A> property of a <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.LiteralMode.Transform> control contains an `<hr>` tag, the tag is removed before the content is sent to a WML device.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="65721-114">如果不受支持的标记包含内容, 则仅删除标记, 并将内容发送到设备或浏览器。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="65721-114">If an unsupported tag contains content, only the tag is removed and the content is sent to the device or browser.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="65721-115">例如, 如果<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A>属性包含`Test`内容`<XYZ>Test</XYZ>`, 则当文本发送`<XYZ>`到`</XYZ>`设备或浏览器时, 将删除和标记。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="65721-115">For example, if the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.Literal.Text%2A> property contains the content `<XYZ>Test</XYZ>`, the `<XYZ>` and `</XYZ>` tags are removed while the text `Test` is sent to the device or browser.</span></span>  
  
   
  
